{"tid":1764673,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"紅磡站免稅店有員工話示威者垃圾、過街老鼠","createTime":"2019-12-01T09:38:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-02T01:05:16.000Z","uid":80936,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"3d80a20f48a3ef0b30beaab31cb7d290b9e2331f","tid":1764673,"uid":80936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T09:38:34.000Z","msg":"啱先行到紅磡站，諗住去個廁所<br />\n我行過呢間免稅鋪門口個陣<br />\n聽到一個曲長頭髮，著住黑西裝嘅員工<br />\n我諗應該係比較大粒嘅<br />\n仲有其中一個著住粉紅色圍裙嘅員工<br />\n望住我同我女朋友講『垃圾，過街老鼠』<br />\n仲要講咗唔止一次<br />\n然後我一望佢哋<br />\n佢地就即刻縮返個頭入去<br />\n然後喺入面繼續講<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/12/01/173740_0f1f8c77822e577a5be85f26f046928d.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F12%2F01%2F173740_0f1f8c77822e577a5be85f26f046928d.JPG&h=4e8ccc73&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8ed2fd3efe6598cde93e85e02fc4f77a5500fa75","tid":1764673,"uid":80936,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T09:40:30.000Z","msg":"唔好意思，更新返<br />\n黑衫係長頭髮，但係冇咁曲<br />\n<br />\n而粉紅色圍裙嗰個就帶住眼鏡<br />\n<br />\n因為佢哋縮返入去<br />\n所以影唔到佢哋相"},{"pid":"06668939bc6b0fc2111f85df7abc749ecf47af26","tid":1764673,"uid":80936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8ed2fd3efe6598cde93e85e02fc4f77a5500fa75","tid":1764673,"uid":80936,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T09:40:30.000Z","msg":"唔好意思，更新返<br />\n黑衫係長頭髮，但係冇咁曲<br />\n<br />\n而粉紅色圍裙嗰個就帶住眼鏡<br />\n<br />\n因為佢哋縮返入去<br />\n所以影唔到佢哋相"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T09:42:02.000Z","msg":"而粉紅色圍裙都係長頭髮嘅"},{"pid":"59773d10d20267b8fc625ced1009fa7087dfce82","tid":1764673,"uid":87305,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T09:42:13.000Z","msg":"唔洗咁在意d少數派<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a81f00427318a060aefe4a62ca15664b430d161d","tid":1764673,"uid":60129,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T09:43:22.000Z","msg":"唔洗理呢啲擺明賺大